 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-vietnam-hold-first-ever-joint-coast-guard-exercise-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>晨标：沐浴在红色的海洋中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-05/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 04:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对市场抛售的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一股市暴跌，债券上涨，原因是对美国可能陷入衰退的担忧导致投资者纷纷逃离风险资产，而押注利率必须迅速下降才能挽救经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国东部创纪录气温，电力需求激增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/high-temperatures-scorch-china-spiking-power-demand-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国东部地区遭遇反常高温，预计江苏和浙江等高度工业化省份的沿海大城市将持续长达10天的高温。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/high-temperatures-scorch-china-spiking-power-demand-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国服务业活动进一步扩张，但外部需求放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-expands-further-external-demand-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，尽管海外需求势头放缓至 11 个月来的最低水平，但在新订单的推动下，7 月份中国服务业活动加速增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:51:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-expands-further-external-demand-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大电动汽车子公司进入破产重组程序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-units-enter-bankruptcy-reorganization-proceedings-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周一表示，在该公司的两个子公司的个人债权人提出破产程序一周后，当地法院已裁定该公司的两个子公司应进入破产并进行重组。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-units-enter-bankruptcy-reorganization-proceedings-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警在萨宾娜浅滩监视菲律宾巡逻艇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-monitors-philippine-patrol-boats-sabina-shoal-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国海警表示，正在监视聚集在有争议的萨比纳浅滩周围的菲律宾巡逻船和渔船，并称中国对南海的南沙群岛拥有“无可争议的主权”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-monitors-philippine-patrol-boats-sabina-shoal-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>日经指数暴跌 13%，股市遭受重创</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-04/</link><description>日本股市暴跌 13%，触及七个月低点，跌幅为 2011 年全球金融危机以来未见。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:37:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>早申：再见软着陆，你好紧急着陆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-04/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 21:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国预计将提议禁止自动驾驶汽车使用中国软件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-expected-propose-barring-chinese-software-autonomous-vehicles-2024-08-04/</link><description>据知情人士透露，美国商务部预计将在未来几周内提议禁止在自动驾驶和联网汽车中使用中国软件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 21:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-expected-propose-barring-chinese-software-autonomous-vehicles-2024-08-04/</guid></item><item><title>游泳：中国终结美国对男子4×100米混合泳接力的统治</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/swimming-china-end-u